We took a group of 35 from a private school....the management Worked with us due to our limited funding..........food was excellent especially the steak and tilapia.....everyone is raving about the place.....service was beyond superior......wait staff immediately served us and cleaned up quickly ....we opened gifts?...they immediately took away wrappings.......staff was also upbeat and attentive...kudos to the Management and Staff of this fine restaurant......many of us will be back often....thank you for allowing us to share in the Christmas Spirit at your place
